synopsis: After killing Alison Sumner and being seemingly killed by Robert Kersey, James Kirby is being transferred to the local morgue. But he isn't dead and kills the coroner and his assistant before escaping into the night. Now anyone who encounters this unstoppable creature is in danger of losing their lives. Who can finally stop this madness, once and for all.
tagline: Following the aftermath of Indestructible, Kirby returns for more vengeance!

synopsis: A film featuring the response by several office workers in response to an Active Shooter attack.
A documentary regarding the Active Shooter phenomenon, and how to protect businesses, schools, and other facilities from the threats of an active assailant.
casting: ['Connor Patrick Griffin', 'Kristina Anderson', 'Dave Hunt', 'Erv Blythe', 'John Cooper', 'Gene Deisinger', 'John Muffler', 'Mary Reed', 'Al Phoenix', 'Ty Williams', 'Terry Wimmer', 'Chris Wood', 'Doris Tucker', 'Jim Tucker', 'Jim Nintzel', 'Emma McMahon', 'George Everly']

synopsis: A young girl, passionate about fashion design, is mysteriously able to enter the 1960s where she encounters her idol, a dazzling wannabe singer. But 1960s London is not what it seems, and time seems to be falling apart with shady consequences.
tagline: When the past lets you in, the truth will come out.
